Created Initially 2019

Single cpp file REWL code for a 6x6 Ising model 
Code has been updated from original to be able to accept arbitrary bounds for energy
In addition to the recombine function which automates rejoining of seperate energy windows

(Initiliazation) mpiCC -o (NAME) Ising.cpp (-lm \needed for Linux systems)

Parameters for Best Results

mpirun -np 3 ./(NAME) 1 1 10 07891
